SUMMARY: New Exhibitions at the Brown County Art Guild
DESCRIPTION:New Exhibitions at the Brown County Art Guild!\n\nMarch 20 - 
 July 17\, 2026\n\nGuild Artist Exhibition and Sale\n\nSpring brings renew
 al\, creativity\, and fresh inspiration. Join us for the Guild Artist Exh
 ibition & Sale showcasing new works from our Guild Artist Members. Experi
 ence the beauty of the season through painting\, color\, and artistic exp
 ression.\n\nMarch 20 – July 17\, 2026\n\nNature’s Symphony\n\nSpecial Exh
 ibition & Sale\n\nDiscover Nature’s Symphony - Special Exhibition & Sale 
 featuring artwork by our talented Guild Artists. Experience how each arti
 st interprets the beauty\, rhythm\, and movement of nature—capturing the 
 harmony of landscapes\, light\, color\, and season in their own unique vo
 ice.\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------
 ------------------------------------\n\nBrown County Art Guild – A not fo
 r profit organization located in the heart of downtown Nashville\, Indian
 a. On display throughout its galleries is a prized collection of historic
  paintings as well as current works for sale from regional award-winning 
 member artists. The Guild also offers artist demonstrations\, workshops\,
  and a variety of events and programs throughout the year.\n\nMarch – Dec
 ember: Monday–Saturday\, 11 – 5 and Sunday\, 12 – 4\n\nWINTER HOURS: Janu
 ary – February: Thursday – Saturday 11 – 5 and Sunday 12-4 or by appointm
 ent.\n\nFor more information\, please call the Guild at 812-988-6185 or v
 isit our website: browncountyartguild.org/ https://browncountyartguild.or
 g/
CATEGORIES:Nashville,Visual-Arts,Gallery
