SUMMARY: Brown County Art Guild 2026 Annual Raffle
DESCRIPTION:Brown County Art Guild Annual Raffle\n\nApril 1 - November 21
 \, 2026\n\nTake a chance to win ‘Painters Point'\, a beautiful original o
 il painting generously donated by Guild Artist\, Allen Hutton. He strives
  to render the fleeting patterns of light and shadow with the simple purp
 ose of preserving the reality of a landscape at a particular moment in ti
 me and season. Allen has achieved numerous awards and his art can be foun
 d in both private and corporate collections across the county.\n\nTickets
 : 1 for $30\, 2 for $50\, or 5 for $100\n\nYour generosity helps the Guil
 d to preserve its historic collection\, promote its award-winning artist 
 members\, and offer workshops and programs throughout the year!\n\nThe dr
 awing of the winning raffle ticket will be held at 3pm on Saturday\, Nove
 mber 21\, 2026\, at the Guild.\n\nThe winner need not be present for the 
 drawing.\n\nPurchase options:\n\nIn person at the Guild\, call 812-988-61
 85 or purchase raffle tickets at:\n\nhttps://browncountyartguild.org/prod
 uct/brown-county-art-guild-annual-raffle/ https://browncountyartguild.org
 /product/brown-county-art-guild-annual-raffle/\n\n-----------------------
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------
 -------------------------\n\nBrown County Art Guild - PO Box 324 - 48 S. 
 Van Buren St. Nashville\, Indiana 47448 - Ph# 812-988-6185\n\n– A not-for
 -profit organization located in the heart of downtown Nashville\, Indiana
 . On display throughout its galleries is a prized collection of historic 
 paintings as well as current works for sale from regional award-winning m
 ember artists. Throughout the year\, the Guild offers artist demonstratio
 ns\, workshops\, and special exhibits.\n\nGuild hours: March-December 202
 6\, Monday – Saturday\, 11 – 5 and Sunday\, 12 – 4 or by appointment.
CATEGORIES:Gallery,Nashville,Tickets,Visual-Arts
