SUMMARY: Mooch the Magnificent
DESCRIPTION:Bridges MAYO\, Reimagining Opera for Kids\, and Stages Bloomi
 ngton have teamed up to produce Lauren Bernofsky's "Mooch the Magnificent
 \," with stage director- Andrew Keeler and musical director-Dr. Lauren Be
 rnofsky. Youth singers and instrumentalists\, ages 8-18\, have been rehea
 rsing alongside professional Reimagining Opera for Kids opera singers and
  IU Jacobs and community musicians to share a tale about a zookeeper\, Or
 lando\, and his assistant\, Mooch. Scored for full orchestra and singers\
 , see what happens when Mooch helps the mechanical animals to disconnect 
 on Tuesday\, April 21 at 7:30PM at Fairview Elementary School gym! This e
 vent is free and family friendly.
