SUMMARY: Quarryland Men's Chorus Spring Concert - By the Numbers
DESCRIPTION:It's the final countdown! The 24th season of QMC is coming to
  an end\, and the chorus is adding another 525\,600 minutes to our long h
 istory with a spring concert that is "By the Numbers!" You won't have to 
 walk 500 miles to enjoy it\, as we are singing right here in Bloomington\
 , at First United Church\, on Saturday\, April 25th at 7:30pm and again o
 n Sunday\, April 26th at 3pm.\n\nNumerical songs abound\, but Quarryland 
 invites you to this curated musical experience where you'll have a millio
 n reasons to laugh\, cry\, cheer\, or just count your blessings. Time aft
 er time\, our chorus sings for a measure of belonging\, personal expressi
 on\, and musical excellence in the LGBTQ+ community. You can count on QMC
  to make it worth your time!\n\nTickets are just $20 general admission\, 
 $10 students\, 17 and under free. Available online\, at the door\, or fro
 m chorus members.\n\nConcert Sponsor:\nIU Credit Union\n\nSeason Sponsors
 :\nShadday Realty Group/Sheetz Century 21\nPsi Iota Xi - Bloomington Thri
 ft Shop
