SUMMARY: Femina Natura
DESCRIPTION:Visit an exhibition of expressive\, nature-inspired paintings
  that explore landscape\, mood\, and the emotional ties between humanity 
 and the natural world. RECEPTION: May 9\, 3PM to 5PM.\n\nGrace/Butedma Go
 nso is a Buryat-Mongol artist living in rural Indiana. She prefers workin
 g in oils with rich colors. Her depictions of her cultural heritage and s
 cenes of rural living are vibrant and expressive. Nature is her greatest 
 inspiration. She enjoys capturing seasonal changes in nature and local fa
 rm and garden images.\n\n
CATEGORIES:
