SUMMARY: The Birds | 15 Years\, 15 Hits
DESCRIPTION:As beautiful blonde Melanie Daniels (Tippi Hedren in her film
  debut) rolls into Bodega Bay in pursuit of eligible bachelor Mitch Brenn
 er (Rod Taylor)\, she is inexplicably attacked by a seagull. Suddenly\, t
 housands of birds are flocking into town\, preying on children and reside
 nts in a disturbing series of attacks. Soon\, Melanie\, Mitch\, his mothe
 r Lydia (Jessica Tandy)\, and local schoolteacher Annie Hayworth (a scene
 -stealing Suzanne Pleshette) are fighting for their lives against a deadl
 y force that can't be explained and can't be stopped in one of Hollywood'
 s most horrific films of nature gone berserk. [119 min\; horror\; English
 ]
