SUMMARY: Your Name Means Dream by Jose Rivera
DESCRIPTION:AI is hauntingly current and a topic that urges us to examine
  its impact.\nWill AI robots soon replace human caregivers for the elderl
 y? With emotionally-charged narrative and poetic dialogue\, José Rivera e
 xamines how we live and form our sense of self in a world that’s increasi
 ngly saturated with technology. It challenges all people\, all identities
  and all faiths. How do we apply morals\, values and ethics when we intro
 duce machine over human?\n\nTheatre legend Diane Kondrat\, who moved west
  after performing theatre for 27 years in Bloomington\, is returning to s
 tar in this production. The role of AI caregiver Stacy will be played by 
 Valerie C. Kilmer who is making her debut with JTB.\n\nWith an extraordin
 ary team of artists and a fascinating topic\, this production promises to
  be a sell-out!
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Theatre
