SUMMARY: Discover Your creative Spirit: Intuitive Inquiry Journaling
DESCRIPTION:Gift yourself a couple of hours on a Saturday afternoon to un
 leash your creative play. Join artist / teacher Sara McQueen in a structu
 red and encouraging space for learning techniques to use your old postcar
 ds\, photos and papers for creating alive and inspiring journal pages. Sa
 ra uses decades of practice in the "Art of Allowing" in her art and her o
 wn journals. She will share a variety of simple collage and visual techni
 ques for exploring your own inner and outer world on the page. No prior "
 artistic or writing" experiences needed. Bring a new or a partially used 
 sketchbook or journal. You are invited but it is not necessary to bring s
 ome photos\, magazine pictures\, or decorative papers you like. All other
  materials provided. Workshop cost $25. Pay on her website or at the day 
 of the event.
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Workshop,Visual-Arts,Live
