SUMMARY: Saturday Sessions
DESCRIPTION:Former teacher turned songwriter\, Geoffrey Livingston starte
 d writing songs in 2024 to reconnect with music and his late father\, Del
 bert. His music and playing are inspired by 70s songwriters\, the discogr
 aphy of the SNES\, and Black American music\, especially Soul and Gospel.
 \n\nSaturday Sessions are causal opportunity for (scheduled) musicians to
  simply play music in our relaxing\, art-filled space. These are not seat
 ed concerts\, but rather a time for shoppers\, diners\, and art-lovers to
  be serenaded while exploring the gallery.\n\nFree parking in the back
