SUMMARY: Intro Level Bellydance Teens & Adults
DESCRIPTION:Say hello to your hips with instructor Donna Carlton. This in
 troductory level class\, based in Egyptian style\, is a great way to get 
 moving and learn fundamentals of a beautiful\, graceful and energetic dan
 ce form. Class meets at Pillar Arts Alliance Center\, located inside Coll
 ege Mall in the former Victoria's Secret location. Plenty of parking and 
 reasonable cost ($15 to drop in or $10 per class when paying for a series
  in advance). Continuing level and private classes available also.
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Class,Dance
