SUMMARY: The Brown County Art Guild Presents\, Art in the Garden - Countr
 yside Blooms & Brushes
DESCRIPTION:Experience the beauty of Art in the Garden – Countryside Bloo
 ms & Brushes!\n\nAn unforgettable annual evening awaits in the heart of B
 rown County. Join the Guild Artist Members as they paint en plein air\, c
 apturing the beauty of the countryside & spring flowers in real time. Wan
 der the Austin Historic Farm\, savor delicious food & relax to the sounds
  of live music. Original artwork & pottery will be available for purchase
 . It’s a celebration of art\, nature\, and community!\n\nSaturday\, May 3
 0\, 2026\n\nJenny & Bill Austin’s Country Retreat\n\n$100 per person\n\n5
  – 8 pm\n\nLive Music\n\nHeavy hors d’oeuvres by Nashville House Catering
  & Cash Bar\n\nGuild Artist Demonstrations\n\nPaintings & Pottery for Sal
 e\n\nParking on Site\n\nRain or Shine\n\nPurchase tickets in person at th
 e Guild\, call 812-988-6185 or online at:\n\nhttps://browncountyartguild.
 org/event/art-in-the-garden-countryside-blooms-brushes/ https://browncoun
 tyartguild.org/event/art-in-the-garden-countryside-blooms-brushes/\n\n___
 ___________________________________________________________________\n\nBr
 own County Art Guild – A not for profit organization located in the heart
  of downtown Nashville\, Indiana. On display throughout its galleries is 
 a prized collection of historic paintings as well as current works for sa
 le from regional award-winning member artists.\n\nAlso offered throughout
  the year are artist demonstrations\, workshops\, and special exhibits.\n
 \nGallery hours March through December 2026\, Monday – Saturday\, 11 – 5 
 and Sunday\, 12 – 4 or by appointment.\n\nIf you would like more informat
 ion\, call 812.988.6185 or visit our web site https://browncountyartguild
 .org/ https://browncountyartguild.org/
CATEGORIES:Nashville,Tickets,Visual-Arts
