SUMMARY: The Red Shoes | 15 Years\, 15 Hits
DESCRIPTION:In one of cinema's most epic backstage dramas\, aspiring ball
 erina Vicky is torn between her dedication to dance and her desire to lov
 e. Her imperious instructor\, Lermontov\, demands she forgets anything bu
 t ballet\, but Vicky begins to fall for the charming young composer Julia
 n Craster. With mounting levels of emotional and physical stress\, Vicky 
 must choose to pursue either her art or her romance\, a decision that car
 ries serious consequences. [135 min\; drama\; English]
