 06428328ed/69e8eed95f82b9dab7838f53/scaled_1024.jpg
X-TKF-CUSTOM-PREVIEW:BCT’s 2nd annual Godzilla Weekend is showcasing this
  giant moth that attacks the whole world with fury! DAY TWO will feature 
