SUMMARY: Raiders of the Lost Ark | 15 Years\, 15 Hits
DESCRIPTION:Accompanied by his feisty\, independent ex-flame Marion Raven
 wood (Karen Allen)\, the two-fisted archaeologist Dr. Indiana Jones (Harr
 ison Ford) embarks on a thrilling quest to locate the the mystical Ark of
  the Covenant in 1936. Indy must discover the Ark before the Nazis do\, a
 nd he has to survive poison\, traps\, snakes\, and treachery to do so. Ex
 plore the darkest jungles of South America\, the bustling marketplaces of
  Cairo\, and a top-secret submarine base with Indy\, Marion\, Brody\, Sal
 lah\, and the whole Indiana gang alongside more bad guys than you can thr
 ow spiders at! [115 min\; action/adventure\, drama\; English]
