SUMMARY: Zach Rushing “Redneck Logic” Comedy Tour
DESCRIPTION:I’m just a Mississippi boy with a loud mouth and a big heart.
  I grew up believing in hard work\, good friends\, and telling it like it
  is\, and I never really grew out of that. Most people know me from my co
 medy\, where I’ve built a career on being unapologetically myself. Whethe
 r I’m on stage for the Not-So-Rich-And-Famous Tour\, raising hell on soci
 al media\, or telling stories that hit a little too close to home\, I try
  to keep it real and keep people laughing.\n\nBut I’m more than just a co
 mic. I run Triple B Outdoors\, where I get to share my love for hunting\,
  fishing\, and the outdoors with folks who live for the same things I do.
  I’m engaged to the love of my life\, and when I’m not on the road\, you’
 ll find me in the woods\, on the water\, or working to grow my businesses
 .\n\nAt the end of the day\, I’m not trying to be famous\, I’m just tryin
 g to be honest\, entertain people\, and maybe inspire a few along the way
 . If you stick around\, you’ll get jokes\, a little wisdom\, and probably
  a few stories you wouldn’t want your grandma to hear.\n\nThis is an 18+ 
 event.
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,In-Person,Tickets,Live
